OL,3,CConfusion around pay deal for nurses
OL,5,FThe Stormont Executive has allocated
OL,6,F#150 million to ministers who were
OL,7,Ffacing shortfalls in meeting public
OL,8,Fsector pay demands.
OL,10,FThe largest allocation is #100 million
OL,11,Fto Health Minister Mike Nesbitt who
OL,12,Fhad asked fellow ministers for #200
OL,13,Fmillion to enable him to deliver a
OL,14,Frecommended uplift to healthcare
OL,15,Fworkers.
OL,17,FNurses have been warning of imminent
OL,18,Fstrike action if a 3.6% increase
OL,19,Frecommended by the independent Pay
OL,20,FReview Body was not met.
