OL,5,FJustice Minister Naomi Long and
OL,6,FInfrastructure Minister Liz Kimmins
OL,7,Fwill get #6.7 million each, which is
OL,8,F50% of what they had requested to fund
OL,9,Fpay awards for police and prison
OL,10,Fofficers and Translink transport
OL,11,Fworkers respectively.
OL,13,FMs O'Neill expressed hope the
OL,14,Fannouncement would lead to a quick
OL,15,Fresolution of the pay dispute with
OL,16,Fnursing staff.
OL,18,F"I think we now have a pathway in
OL,19,Fterms of being able to deal with the
OL,20,Fhealth pay issue," she said. "And I
OL,21,Fthink it's a positive step forward.
