OL,5,F"Equally, we had the similar
OL,6,Fconversation around education, and
OL,7,Fwe've been able to allocate a further
OL,8,F#37 million for our teachers, again
OL,9,Ffor the purposes of teachers' pay. So
OL,10,Fcollectively, #137 million today
OL,11,Facross health and education."
OL,13,FShe added: "The health minister said
OL,14,Fhe needed #200 million to deliver pay
OL,15,Fparity (matching awards recommended
OL,16,Felsewhere in the UK). He's found #100m
OL,17,Fand we have found #100m, so there is
OL,18,Fthe pot in which he's dealing with.
