OL,5,F"But obviously I'm sensitive to the
OL,6,Ffact that he needs to speak to the
OL,7,Funions now in terms of how that will
OL,8,Fbe delivered. So it's over to him ...
OL,9,Fbut he has the pathway now and he has
OL,10,Fthe money to back it up."
OL,12,FMs O'Neill said ministers were
OL,13,Fdetermined to "break the cycle" of
OL,14,Fannual wrangles over pay. She said the
OL,15,FExecutive's new three-year budget,
OL,16,Fwhich will be drawn up in the coming
OL,17,Fmonths, would include "upfront"
OL,18,Fcommitments to cover future pay awards
OL,19,Ffor health workers.
