OL,10,F"We have been very clear that it is
OL,11,Fessential that public sector workers
OL,12,Fare paid appropriately," she said.
OL,14,F"We are acutely aware of the pressures
OL,15,Fon budgets and the significant
OL,16,Fchallenges that departments face.
