OL,5,F"We know, and to be very clear, we
OL,6,Fknow that words are not enough. It
OL,7,Frequires action. It requires the
OL,8,FExecutive to be clear that we do have
OL,9,Fthe backs of our hard-working public
OL,10,Fsector workers, and that must mean
OL,11,Ffinding the support that is needed in
OL,12,Forder to address these issues.
OL,14,F"People should not have to fight for
OL,15,Ffair pay. And every single year we
OL,16,Ffind ourselves in the situation of the
OL,17,Fchallenge to try to find that, so that
OL,18,Fis something that we are determined to
OL,19,Ftry to resolve in a better way moving
OL,20,Fforward as well."
